'''Zeraora''' (Japanese: '''ゼラオラ''' ''Zeraora'') is a {{ct|Lightning}} Basic Pokémon card in [[Pokémon Trading Card Game Pocket]]. It was first released as part of the {{TCGP|Extradimensional Crisis}} expansion.

